Chidi Mokeme (a mụrụ ya n'ụbọchị nke 17 n'ọnwa Maachị n'afọ 1972) bụ onye na-eme ihe nkiri na onye na-eme ihe ngosi. O si Oba na Idemili South LGA nke Anambra steeti, ndịda ọwụwa anyanwụ Naịjirịa. Ọ bụ onye nhazi nke Gulder Ultimate Search Reality-show.
Chidi bụ onye ntụziaka nke nke ihe ngosi Television Gulder Ultimate Search maka afọ ole na ole.
